@startuml SSO_Navigation_Flow

title SSO Navigation Between Main Platform and Learning Platform

actor "Researcher" as User
participant "Main Platform\nDashboard" as MainUI
participant "Auth Service" as Auth
participant "SSO Service" as SSO
participant "Learning Platform\nDashboard" as LearnUI
database "Redis Cache" as Redis
database "PostgreSQL" as DB

== Initial Login to Main Platform ==

User -> MainUI: Access platform.com
activate MainUI

MainUI -> Auth: POST /auth/login\n(email, password)
activate Auth

Auth -> DB: Verify credentials
activate DB
DB --> Auth: User found (role=RESEARCHER)
deactivate DB

Auth -> Auth: Generate JWT Token\n(userId, role, permissions)

Auth -> Redis: Store session\n(token, userId, expiry)
activate Redis
Redis --> Auth: Stored
deactivate Redis

Auth --> MainUI: JWT Token + User Data
deactivate Auth

MainUI --> User: Show Researcher Dashboard
deactivate MainUI

== Navigation to Learning Platform ==

User -> MainUI: Click "Go to Learning Platform"
activate MainUI

MainUI -> SSO: Request SSO Token\n(Authorization: Bearer <JWT>)
activate SSO

SSO -> Auth: Validate JWT Token
activate Auth
Auth -> Redis: Check token validity
activate Redis
Redis --> Auth: Token valid
deactivate Redis
Auth --> SSO: User verified
deactivate Auth

SSO -> SSO: Generate SSO Token\n(short-lived, 5 min)

SSO -> Redis: Store SSO Token\n(sso_token, userId, expiry=5min)
activate Redis
Redis --> SSO: Stored
deactivate Redis

SSO --> MainUI: SSO Token
deactivate SSO

MainUI -> MainUI: Build redirect URL\nlearn.platform.com/sso?token=<sso_token>

MainUI --> User: Redirect to Learning Platform
deactivate MainUI

== SSO Authentication on Learning Platform ==

User -> LearnUI: GET /sso?token=<sso_token>
activate LearnUI

LearnUI -> SSO: Validate SSO Token
activate SSO

SSO -> Redis: Check SSO token
activate Redis
Redis --> SSO: Token valid + userId
deactivate Redis

SSO -> DB: Get user details
activate DB
DB --> SSO: User data
deactivate DB

SSO -> SSO: Generate Learning Platform JWT\n(userId, role, learning_permissions)

SSO -> Redis: Delete used SSO token\n(one-time use)
activate Redis
Redis --> SSO: Deleted
deactivate Redis

SSO -> Redis: Store learning session
Redis --> SSO: Stored
deactivate Redis

SSO --> LearnUI: Learning JWT Token + User Data
deactivate SSO

LearnUI --> User: Show Learning Dashboard\n(No password required!)
deactivate LearnUI

== User Activity on Learning Platform ==

User -> LearnUI: Browse challenges
activate LearnUI
LearnUI --> User: Challenge list
deactivate LearnUI

User -> LearnUI: Complete challenge
activate LearnUI

LearnUI -> DB: Update progress\nEarn points, badges
activate DB
DB --> LearnUI: Updated
deactivate DB

LearnUI -> DB: Sync to main profile\n(reputation, skills)
DB --> LearnUI: Synced
deactivate DB

LearnUI --> User: Challenge completed!
deactivate LearnUI

== Return to Main Platform ==

User -> LearnUI: Click "Back to Main Platform"
activate LearnUI

LearnUI -> SSO: Request reverse SSO token
activate SSO

SSO -> Auth: Validate learning JWT
activate Auth
Auth --> SSO: Valid
deactivate Auth

SSO -> SSO: Generate reverse SSO token

SSO -> Redis: Store reverse SSO token
activate Redis
Redis --> SSO: Stored
deactivate Redis

SSO --> LearnUI: Reverse SSO Token
deactivate SSO

LearnUI --> User: Redirect to platform.com/sso?token=<token>
deactivate LearnUI

User -> MainUI: GET /sso?token=<reverse_sso_token>
activate MainUI

MainUI -> SSO: Validate reverse SSO token
activate SSO
SSO -> Redis: Check token
activate Redis
Redis --> SSO: Valid
deactivate Redis
SSO --> MainUI: User verified
deactivate SSO

MainUI -> DB: Get updated user data\n(with new reputation from learning)
activate DB
DB --> MainUI: Updated user profile
deactivate DB

MainUI --> User: Show Main Dashboard\n(Updated reputation visible!)
deactivate MainUI

== Session Expiry Handling ==

group Session Expired
    User -> LearnUI: Action after session expired
    activate LearnUI
    
    LearnUI -> Auth: Validate JWT
    activate Auth
    Auth -> Redis: Check token
    activate Redis
    Redis --> Auth: Token expired
    deactivate Redis
    Auth --> LearnUI: 401 Unauthorized
    deactivate Auth
    
    LearnUI --> User: Redirect to login\n(Session expired)
    deactivate LearnUI
end

note right of SSO
  SSO Token Properties:
  - Short-lived (5 minutes)
  - One-time use only
  - Deleted after validation
  - Cannot be reused
  - Secure random generation
end note

note right of Redis
  Session Storage:
  - Main platform JWT (1 hour)
  - Learning platform JWT (1 hour)
  - SSO tokens (5 minutes)
  - Refresh tokens (7 days)
end note

note right of DB
  Profile Sync:
  - Learning progress → Main profile
  - Badges earned → Visible on main
  - Skills acquired → Reputation boost
  - Challenges completed → Stats
end note

@enduml
